\chapter{Why you should use data science?}
\label{chap:ch1}


\subsection{Objectives}
By the end of this chapter, you will be able to:
\begin{itemize}
\item Distinguish between three applications of statistics and identify
situations in which each is appropriate
\item Distinguish between discrete and continuous variables and cite
examples of each
\item Identify and describe three levels of measurement and cite examples
